name "lem:supp_in_sing"

\end_inset

Let 
\begin_inset Formula $\mu$
\end_inset

 be a 
\begin_inset Formula ${\cal F}$
\end_inset

-invariant probability measure on 
\begin_inset Formula $T^{1}M$
\end_inset

.
 Suppose 
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda(v)=0$
\end_inset

 for 
\begin_inset Formula $\mu$
\end_inset

 almost every 
\begin_inset Formula $v\in T^{1}M$
\end_inset

, then 
\begin_inset Formula ${\rm supp(\mu)\subset\Sing}.$
\end_inset


\end_layout

