name "thm:geometric-potential-Bowen"

\end_inset

The geometric potential 
\begin_inset Formula $\varphi^{u}$
\end_inset

 has the Bowen property with respect to 
\begin_inset Formula $\gt(\eta)$
\end_inset

 for any 
\begin_inset Formula $\eta>0$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

